ersion)</p>\n<p><code>set_target_properties(caffe2_gpu PROPERTIES INTERFACE_INCLUDE_DIRECTORIES \"${_IMPORT_PREFIX}/include\" INTERFACE_LINK_LIBRARIES \"caffe2::cudart;caffe2;caffe2::cufft;caffe2::curand;caffe2::cudnn;/usr/local/cuda/lib64/libculibos.a;caffe2::cublas\" ) </code><br>\nThe absolute link to /usr/local/cuda/lib64/libculibos.a probably causes some of the problems that are solved by compiling locally.</p>", "body_text": "\ud83d\udc1b Bug\n\nThe Caffe2Targets.cmake file included in the nightly builds includes the code (from the current version)\nset_target_properties(caffe2_gpu PROPERTIES INTERFACE_INCLUDE_DIRECTORIES \"${_IMPORT_PREFIX}/include\" INTERFACE_LINK_LIBRARIES \"caffe2::cudart;caffe2;caffe2::cufft;caffe2::curand;caffe2::cudnn;/usr/local/cuda/lib64/libculibos.a;caffe2::cublas\" ) \nThe absolute link to /usr/local/cuda/lib64/libculibos.a probably causes some of the problems that are solved by compiling locally.", "body": "## \ud83d\udc1b Bug\r\n\r\n<!-- A clear and concise description of what the bug is. -->\r\n\r\nThe Caffe2Targets.cmake file included in the nightly builds includes the code (from the current version)\r\n\r\n`set_target_properties(caffe2_gpu PROPERTIES\r\n  INTERFACE_INCLUDE_DIRECTORIES \"${_IMPORT_PREFIX}/include\"\r\n  INTERFACE_LINK_LIBRARIES \"caffe2::cudart;caffe2;caffe2::cufft;caffe2::curand;caffe2::cudnn;/usr/local/cuda/lib64/libculibos.a;caffe2::cublas\"\r\n)\r\n`\r\nThe absolute link to /usr/local/cuda/lib64/libculibos.a probably causes some of the problems that are solved by compiling locally.\r\n"}